        "name" => "The Magician",
        "upright_keyword" => "Willpower, Desire, Resourcefulness, Skills, Ability, Focus, Performance",
        "reversed_keyword" => "Manipulation, Cunning, Trickery, Wasted talent, Delusion, Deception",
        "astrology" => "Mercury",
        "element" => "Air Element",
        "image_key" => "01_Magician",
        "content" => "The Magician is a tarot card filled with symbolic meaning. The figure in the center depicts a person pointing one hand to the sky and the other to the ground, as if saying 'as above, so below'. This is a more complex phrase, summarizing that the earth reflects heaven, the outside reflects the inside, the microcosm reflects the macrocosm, and the earth reflects God. This can also be interpreted as the Magician symbolizing the ability to act as an intermediary between the upper world and the contemporary human world. On his table, the Magician also wields all the tarot cards. This symbolizes the Magician's connection of the four elements - earth, water, air, and fire. The infinity symbol above his head represents the infinite possibilities created by will.",
        "upright_content" => "The Magician represents pure willpower. With the power of the elements and the power of the suit, he shapes the innate potential of the Fool into existence with the power of desire. He is the link between heaven and earth, as he understands the meaning behind 'as above, so below' - thoughts and the world are mere reflections of each other. Remember, you are powerful; create your inner world, and the outer will follow. When you see the Magician, it may mean it's time to unleash your full potential without hesitation. This could be in your new job, new venture, new romance, or other areas. It indicates that now is the time for action, and any signs of hesitation mean missing the opportunity to be your best self. Choices must be made, and these choices may bring about significant changes. Utilize some of the Magician's powers to create the world you desire most.",
        "reversed_content" => "When you receive the reversed Magician, it may indicate it's time to implement some changes. Upright, the Magician represents true power; reversed, the Magician is the master of illusions. The magic he performs is one of deception and trickery. You may be drawn in by his performance art, but behind it may lie manipulative intentions driven by selfishness. Getting this card may mean someone is pretending to have your best interests at heart when, in fact, quite the opposite is true. Consider whether this reversed Magician is in your circle, or it may also represent your current state of mind. It could suggest you might be obsessed with power, which could lead to misguided, reckless decisions, ultimately leading to your downfall.",
        "upright_love" => "As with its general meanings, the Magician tarot card in love suggests making things clear. Skills, creativity, desire, and determination will bring success in love. If you're seeking love, the Magician advises taking action and creating opportunities to meet the person you desire. Since the Magician in tarot also represents resourcefulness and skill, it's essential to ensure there's no deception or illusion at play. For singles and couples alike, the Magician brings excitement and a desire to experiment.",
        "reversed_love" => "The reversed Magician tarot card in love can indicate that not everything is as it seems. When it comes to new relationships, you may want to ensure you truly understand your new partner. Even if they seem perfect, it could be a deception or a performance. Alternatively, the reversed Magician in love could indicate a lack of confidence or willpower, or an inability to express yourself in relationships, causing insecurity in romance and love.",
        "upright_career" => "Opportunities may be present for you, and if you take decisive action, you may be able to capitalize on them. The Magician is a card of manifestation, indicating that if you have the desire and commitment to pursue anything you want in your career, you are likely to find success. Look behind any successful individual, and you'll likely find strong willpower and drive; this is the root of all ambition. The same applies if you're considering entrepreneurship; harness that drive and maintain the motivation to achieve your dream career. Sometimes, if this card represents another person, such as a colleague or business partner, you may need to exercise caution as they may not be everything they appear to be.",
        "reversed_career" => "Are you truly leveraging all your talents right now? Are there skills in your current job that are being overlooked? If you truly want to unlock your full potential, then you may have many opportunities for advancement. You may feel this but perhaps are too afraid to take the risk, as it might be a bold move. You need to carefully examine what the real risks are and understand if your fears are genuinely grounded in reality or if they stem from different sources. Sometimes this card can also indicate that people in your workplace may not be entirely honest, or there may be hidden agendas. If your intuition tells you this, trust it; be wary of how much you share around them.",
        "upright_finances" => "More financial opportunities are available now, and you may just need to pursue them with enthusiasm. The Magician uses many tools to manifest his will. Try to look at the tools you have available; they could be your keys right now. What skills do you have? What abilities are you not currently utilizing? Creativity can yield results.",
        "reversed_finances" => "If your financial situation isn't quite what you desire right now, it may be because you're not giving it your all. You may have energies or talents going to waste, and you just need to bolster your confidence and put yourself out there. You may lack the willpower to turn talents into money. Exercise caution when sharing detailed information about your financial situation with others.",
        "yes_no" => "The Magician symbolizes action and power in your life. Its positive connotations suggest someone who is articulate, skilled in various aspects of communication. This card advises moving forward with your strong willpower and taking action. The answer to your question is yes.",
        "past" => "Your confidence and creativity enabled you to effectively turn your ideas into reality. You gained success through wisdom and skillful execution.",
        "present" => "Currently, your knowledge and skills are needed to influence the changes happening. To make the changes beneficial, you must act correctly.",
        "future" => "The future ahead of you is uncertain, with risks and opportunities abound. Possibilities will be influenced by the friendships you nurture and the support you receive from loved ones. A victory or creative success may bring you a fresh start.",
