        "name" => "The High Priestess",
        "upright_keyword" => "Subconscious, Intuition, Mystery, Spirituality, Higher power, Inner voice",
        "reversed_keyword" => "Suppressed intuition, Hidden motives, Superficiality, Confusion, Cognitive dissonance",
        "astrology" => "Moon",
        "element" => "Water Element",
        "image_key" => "02_High_Priestess",
        "content" => "She sits between the two pillars of Solomon's temple, Jachin and Boaz. Jachin (on the right) is often referred to as the Pillar of Establishment, while Boaz (on the left) is the Pillar of Strength. The pillars also depict the duality of nature; masculine and feminine, good and evil, passive and active. The High Priestess sits between the two, indicating her role as a mediator in the depths of reality. She is the third pillar—the path between the two. She sees these two pillars as equal, with knowledge to be gained in both worlds. You'll also notice she wears the crown of Isis, which may signify her allegiance to magic. The High Priestess with the solar cross indicates her connection to the seasons of the earth and the earth itself. The crescent moon at her feet, seen in many depictions of the Virgin Mary, signifies her mastery over her emotions.",
        "upright_content" => "The High Priestess speaks to inner knowledge. Her presence may suggest it's time to listen to your intuition rather than prioritizing your intellect and consciousness. When the High Priestess appears, it can portray an archetype known as the Divine Feminine, understanding and mastering the mysteries of deep unknown answers; religion, self, nature. She represents an intuitive person who begins to open up to her or his spirituality. Meditation, prayer, and new spiritual work are indicated. The card itself shows a nocturnal scene, indicating the world she protects and guards may seem frightening at first glance but may guide us into personal growth. When she appears, she is calling you to listen to her messages and follow her into your own depths. You need to search within yourself for the answers you seek. The answer to your question lies inside, not outside.",
        "reversed_content" => "When the High Priestess appears reversed, it may indicate difficulty in heeding your intuition. Now is the time for meditation and trying new approaches, as rational methods may not work. Something has been telling you to follow your intuition, but you may have been ignoring the signal. There's much confusion around you, and your actions may be contrary to what you know to be right. Never be afraid to ask yourself questions; they may point you in a new direction, a path to your inner self and your personal values.",
        "upright_love" => "The High Priestess in a love tarot reading can suggest almost imperceptible and unconscious changes in a person's emotional state. A calm exterior can conceal strong emotions, and even seemingly simple dates can turn into intense passion. In love tarot, the High Priestess card indicates a need for patience and trusting your intuition. Be honest with others and yourself, allowing hidden things to come to the surface. In a relationship, the High Priestess shows increasing intimacy and openness. In love tarot, this card indicates that honesty is crucial to making your relationship as strong as possible.",
        "reversed_love" => "The High Priestess is the guardian of your intuition, indicating it can be a powerful indicator that you need to trust your feelings in love and romance. Difficulties arise when you ignore your intuition and only follow your consciousness. The meaning of the High Priestess in love can also indicate that you must tread carefully to be truly honest. Avoid taking actions or speaking to please your loved one. This will only lead to resentment.",
        "upright_career" => "When it comes to your career, the High Priestess may signify a period of education or higher learning. You may be returning to school for training. If you're in a creative field, this card can also offer new inspiration for your work. When making significant choices about your future career or projects, the High Priestess also advises relying on your intuition. There may be plenty of information available to assist you. Sometimes, this card can also indicate the appearance of a mentor or guide who can help you progress further in your work.",
        "reversed_career" => "Regarding your current work situation, you may not be getting all the information. Are people keeping you in the dark? As a result, you may feel isolated and may be losing connections with colleagues. It could also be that in making career decisions, you haven't been listening to your intuition. Despite intuition suggesting they don't have your best interests at heart, did you choose to trust them? Despite intuition telling you this job isn't right for you, are you still engaged in work you despise? This card can also suggest a colleague with hidden agendas; be cautious around others. Enthusiastic behavior may conceal dangers.",
        "upright_finances" => "Because the High Priestess is associated with mystery and the unknown, be cautious discussing your financial situation with others. This card suggests keeping your financial affairs hidden. Alternatively, if you have an opportunity to use your finances, your intuition will know whether it's a good choice. Take some time to explore your feelings; if there are warning signs, things will feel off. Listen to those feelings.",
        "reversed_finances" => "Are you signing contracts, loans, getting mortgages, or investing in something? You may be missing some details. The reversed High Priestess in financial tarot means you haven't fully grasped all the information needed to make the right, educated decisions. Make sure you have someone you can trust who can give you all the facts.",
        "yes_no" => "The High Priestess is a spiritually intuitive woman full of mystery, wisdom, and understanding. She represents things yet undiscovered in your life, so the answer to your question is unclear.",
        "past" => "You've been in need of new experiences, possibly wandering somewhere outside of your comfort zone. If you've lacked support in important areas of your life, you should consider investing time in new friends and new ideas. You're entering a new period, but you may need help from others.",
        "present" => "The creative abilities you possess that have been undiscovered or suppressed need to be expressed. Seek out spiritual mentors who will help you realize the full potential of your spiritual or artistic abilities. To get what you want, you need to overcome your fear of commitment.",
        "future" => "You'll reap real rewards, but only if you continue to maintain discipline and motivation. If you refuse to be deterred in your attempts, your future is bright. Follow your intuition, and you'll move towards long-lasting fulfillment and success.",
    ],
